# Plan: Add PixelArt Provider to Vercel AI SDK

## Context

We need to add a new fictional "PixelArt" AI provider (`@ai-sdk/pixelart`) to the Vercel AI SDK monorepo. This provider **only** supports image generation (no text/chat/embeddings). It follows the exact same patterns as existing providers (OpenAI, Google, Anthropic) but with a minimal footprint — only the image model implementation is needed. The provider uses `https://api.pixelart.ai/v1` as its base URL, authenticates via `PIXELART_API_KEY`, and supports custom settings: `size`, `style` ("pixel" | "retro" | "8bit"), and `pixelDensity` (number).

