| Utility | File | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `postJsonToApi` | provider-utils | POST JSON to image generation endpoint |
| `createJsonResponseHandler` | provider-utils | Parse successful API response with schema |
| `createJsonErrorResponseHandler` | provider-utils | Parse error responses |
